<p>Be in with the chance to win a ski holiday for two during the 2022-23 ski season at the <span><strong>Hotel Blumental in Murren - Switzerland. Holiday includes:</strong></span></p>
<p>✔️Half board accommodation for 7 nights </p>
<p>✔️Flights, transfers and lift passes, courtesy of <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.myswitzerland.com/en-gb/" target="_blank">Switzerland Tourism</a></p>
<p>✔️ 1 weeks clothing rental, courtesy of <span><a rel="noopener" href="https://ecoski.co.uk/" target="_blank">EcoSki</a>.</span><span></span></p>
<h3>Enter by 17:00 on Sunday 16th October 2022.</h3>
<p><span>At Inghams, we’ve been taking people on ski holidays since 1934. Beginning with a single trip to Austria, we now sell holidays to 75 resorts across 7 countries. Every detail and interaction is built on over 85 years of passion and experience so you can trust us to deliver an incredible holiday. </span></p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Exclusive Snow Show deals - save an extra £50pp</h2>
<p>Enjoy extra great value with savings of an additional <strong>£50pp. </strong>To redeem the extra £50pp saving call us<strong> 01483 945 084<span class="InfinityNumber"> </span></strong>quoting <strong>SNOWSHOW50</strong>. </p>
<h3>Book by 31st October 2022. </h3>
